                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseZero" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingZero" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="fst-italic">From Keahole (Kona) International Airport: Head east on Keahole Airport Rd. Turn left at traffic light onto HI-19. Follow HI-19 to Spencer Beach Park Rd. (26.1 mi) Turn left onto HI-270 (0.4 mi) Turn left onto Spencer Beach Park Rd. (0.3 mi) Destination will be second right on Spencer Beach Park Rd. (Approximately 32 minute drive 27.5 mi)</p>
